   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Year 24 of Antoninus Caesar the lord, Phamenoth 10. Give from the account of Julius Theon the functioning archidikastes and Julius Theon, alias Tryphon, for wages from the months Hadrianus to Mecheir inclusive, for three months, one hundred and twenty drachmas, total 120 drachmas. (2nd. hd.) Give the 120 drachmas."</ab>
